| Compatible Django Version | Specifically tested |
| ------------------------- | ------------------- |
| `4.0`                     | :heavy_check_mark:  |
| `4.1`                     | :heavy_check_mark:  |
| `4.2`                     | :heavy_check_mark:  |
| `5.0`                     | :heavy_check_mark:  |
| `5.1`                     | :heavy_check_mark:  |
